--------------------------------------
     DesignerPlus for Delphi
--------------------------------------

DesignerPlus is an freeware expert for 
Delphi IDE. It allows you to work with 
controls on forms, that is to change 
positions, size, TabOrder properties 
and some other things. DesignerPlus 
makes you feel more comfortable during 
work in Delphi IDE. In most cases it 
gives you an opportunity to work only 
with a help of hot keys without using 
a mouse.
